 Title\tViews\tDuration\tDollar/View\tTotal Revenue\tDescription & CTAs\tProduct URLs Copy This YouTube Strategy, It'll Blow Up Your Business\t128,569\t8:15\t$1.80*\t~$231K\t\"Work with me - https://film-booth.com/ytgs?video=7L289H87gIU Track sales from your videos - https://www.getrevtrack.com/?video=7L289H87gIU Get my free weekly advice https://film-booth.com/booth-club?video=7L289H87gIU\"\tPrimary: film-booth.com/ytgs Secondary: getrevtrack.com Lead Magnet: booth-club 5 NEW AI That Just Changed YouTube Forever\t90,253\t16:02\t$8.00*\t~$722K\t\"Work With Me - https://www.film-booth.com/ytgs?video=w7KoMQb2STE Get RevTrack - https://www.getrevtrack.com/?video=w7KoMQb2STE LIVE STREAM RECORDING - https://youtube.com/live/bB4uCPF5_80\"\tPrimary: film-booth.com/ytgs Secondary: getrevtrack.com Affiliate: Loveable How To Build A Profitable YouTube Channel In 30 Days\t24,706\t17:28\t$4.00*\t~$99K\t\"Work with me - https://film-booth.com/ytgs?video=bl6P7wyhmrw RevTrack - Track Sales From Videos - https://www.getrevtrack.com/?video=bl6P7wyhmrw Free ai video planning bot https://film-booth.com/ai-planning-bot?video=bl6P7wyhmrw\"\tPrimary: film-booth.com/ytgs Secondary: getrevtrack.com Lead Magnet: ai-planning-bot Special High-Converting Video (Example)\t474\tN/A\t$21.00\t~$10K\tUltra-targeted content addressing specific buyer pain point (warm audience depletion)\tPrimary: film-booth.com/ytgs $1,000,000 YouTube Strategy\t63,949\t25:56\t$4.50*\t~$288K\tDeep-dive strategy video positioned as his program outline\tPrimary: film-booth.com/ytgs *Estimated based on Ed's stated performance metrics and revenue figures 🎯 CORE MONETIZATION FRAMEWORK The 6-Step Sales System Integration: Step\tAction\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tImplementation Time 1. Hook Formula\t3-part intro (problem + credibility + <15 sec)\tScript outline\t15-20% viewer retention past intro\t30 minutes 2. Killer Insight\tFront-load best point after intro\tCore teaching point\t60%+ retention through first third\t1 hour 3. 90-Second CTA\tAsk for email signup early\tLead magnet ready\t1-10% click-through rate\t15 minutes 4. Make Info Feel New\tCreate tools/visuals/frameworks\tContent concept\tHigher engagement, more shares\t2-4 hours 5. Triple CTA Strategy\tAsk 3 times (90 sec, middle, end)\tSame CTA repeated\t3-8% total click-through rate\t30 minutes 6. End Screen Direction\tPoint to high-converting video\tAnalytics data\t20% end screen CTR\t15 minutes 💰 REVENUE STREAM ARCHITECTURE Primary Offer: YouTube Growth System (film-booth.com/ytgs) Price Point: High-ticket ($5,000+) Sales Method: Application → Waitlist → Limited enrollment Conversion Strategy: Email nurture → Direct sales page Revenue Impact: 70% of total income Secondary Offer: RevTrack Software (getrevtrack.com) Price Point: SaaS subscription Sales Method: Free trial → Paid conversion Conversion Strategy: Demonstrated in videos as case study Revenue Impact: 25% of total income Lead Magnets: AI Planning Bot (ai-planning-bot) Booth Club Newsletter (booth-club) Free tools demonstrated in videos 🔄 THE CONTENT CLUSTER LOOP SYSTEM Ed's genius is creating a 4-5 video referral network that works like this: YouTube identifies 4-5 videos with high viewer satisfaction These videos pull 70-100 views per hour continuously New viewer discovers Video A → YouTube suggests Videos B, C, D Each video has same CTA → drives to same funnel End screens point to highest-converting video in the cluster Loop continues 24/7 without new content needed Key Metrics for Cluster Success: Return Viewers: Only YouTube Studio metric Ed tracks Dollar Per View: $4-21 depending on audience temperature Click-Through Rate: 1% average, 8-10% with proper CTAs About Page Link: His #1 revenue generator ($500K lifetime) 🎯 THE \"APPLE PIE\" STRATEGY Ed's channel is like an apple pie where every slice is apple (solves same problem for same person): ❌ WRONG: Mixed content (confidence + relationships + communication) Result: Low binge-watching, scattered audience, poor conversions ✅ RIGHT: Unified content (YouTube growth for businesses only) Result: High binge rate, targeted audience, strong conversions Implementation: All videos address YouTube growth for business owners Every video leads to same offer (YouTube coaching program) Consistent messaging about sales/leads/business metrics 📈 ADVANCED TACTICS & SECRETS 1. The $500K About Page Link Location: Channel About section Strategy: Single link to main offer (no social media links) Performance: Consistently top 3 click source Revenue: $500K+ lifetime value 2. Community Post Strategy (80/20 Rule) 80% Value: Tips, insights, behind-scenes 20% Promotion: Flash sales, limited bonuses Frequency: 5 posts per week during testing Result: Maintained business during 6-month video hiatus 3. Email Automation Sequence Day 1: Welcome + immediate offer exposure Days 2-20: 10 emails (5 value + 5 case studies) Strategy: Every email has P.S. with soft CTA Open Rate: Same on day 1 and day 20 (meaning not enough emails) 4. Revenue Tracking Over Views Ed completely ignores YouTube Studio except for Return Viewers metric: Views: Irrelevant vanity metric Revenue Per View: Primary success indicator Business Dashboard: Tracks clicks, emails, sales from each video Decision Making: Doubles down on revenue-generating content only ⚠️ CRITICAL SUCCESS FACTORS DO This: Track business metrics, not YouTube metrics Ask for email signup in first 90 seconds Make every video solve the same core problem Use your about page link strategically Create content clusters that refer to each other Focus on return viewers as primary KPI DON'T Do This: Chase views over revenue Create content on multiple topics Wait until end of video for CTA Optimize for entertainment over education Ignore business metrics in favor of YouTube analytics Create content without tracking revenue impact 🛠️ IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP Week 1: Foundation Setup Set up tracking system (RevTrack or alternative) Create single high-ticket offer Build email automation sequence Optimize about page with single link Week 2-5: Content Testing Phase Create 8-12 videos on same topic/problem Mix formats (deep dive, tips, case studies, tools) Include 90-second CTA in every video Track which videos generate most revenue Week 6-8: Optimization Phase Identify top 4-5 performing videos Point all end screens to highest converter Double down on winning formats Eliminate low-performing content types Week 9-12: Scale Phase Create \"mega video\" based on learnings Build referral network between top videos Implement community post strategy Focus on return viewer growth 📋 Complete Knowledge Base Document: Ed Lawrence YouTube Monetization Strategy Analysis This comprehensive analysis shows exactly how Ed Lawrence built a $300K-$500K monthly YouTube business by optimizing for BUYERS not VIEWERS - a fundamental shift that 99% of creators miss. The key is treating YouTube as a business platform, not an entertainment platform, and measuring success through revenue metrics rather than vanity metrics. Create a AI agent prompt that would be able to make this a template. So I can put any topic and use subscriber.AI will subscriber.com to create video scripts, but I want to be able to have the channel. Optimized, in the way that at Lawrence has based on what he shared in his video and his channel descriptions. We want to be able to have clusters of videos permitted call to action timing for each script. The length of the time for each script, a template for each script based on Ed's optimized model. So create a detailed knowledge base and a detailed AR agent prompt. I can put the prompt inside of Google. Sheets and run bulk channel creations or have an AI. Agent created as AG, P, T, so please make this as detailed as possible specifically on everything. Ed Lawrence has shared if you were launching and running a channel looking to target specifically buyers. So we need to know how to set the channel niche. We need to know how to set keywords. Any 